         <abstract>
            <p>Corresponding to the so-called Greek pseudo-Athanasian Syntagma,
            transmitted as Didascalia of the 318 Nicene Fathers, for which a Greek Vorlage could be proposed.
            Incorporated within the Senodos (<ref type="work" corresp="LIT1313Discou">CAe 1313</ref>), it has a later, although recensionally much different, equivalent in the
            Haymānota ʾabaw, certainly depending upon an Arabic Vorlage (<ref type="work" corresp="LIT6819Teachi318HA">CAe 6819</ref>).</p>
